### Analytics Endpoints Testing
### Make sure backend is running on port 9000

@baseUrl = http://localhost:9000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Sales Analytics (Last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/sales?startDate=2025-11-28&endDate=2025-12-28
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get Purchase Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/purchases?startDate=2025-11-28&endDate=2025-12-28
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Inventory Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Profit Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/profit?startDate=2025-11-28&endDate=2025-12-28
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Dashboard Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Notes:
# - Replace {{token}} with your actual JWT token
# - Backend must be running on port 9000
# - Ensure you have ADMIN or MANAGER role
# - Date format: YYYY-MM-DD
